data.description: This country charmer is nestled on an oversized .60 acre lot, with powered up (Electric, A/C & Heat) metal workshop, pool deck, NEW ROOF IN 2023 ON BOTH HOME AND SHOP, and NO BACK NEIGHBORS! The home offers spacious tiled living areas and enclosed sunroom with access to the back deck where you can peacefully relax and wait for the frequent visits from the local deer. You won’t believe the low tax rate and HOA dues; and for those of you with a green thumb - check out this list of mature vegetation!! Banana tree, pear tree, peach tree, lemon tree, 2 pecan trees, loquat tree, persimmon and a grape vine! Make this your little piece of paradise and call today to schedule a private tour!
